show.title: A Vow Of Joy And Sorrow
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/5GFYUt
show.description: Roger Nandlall, an abstinent CEO, cannot survive New Year's Eve because of his Yang body. However, he unexpectedly discovered that Brenda Cameron, a poor college student, was the only person in the world who can cure his Yin body. To survive, Roger married Brenda domineeringly. After learning that Brenda's life would be in danger after curing him, Roger, who slowly fell in love with Brenda, was faced with a painful choice between life and death...
